#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean_distances.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean\\_distances"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:1 of
msgid ""
"Considering the rows of X (and Y=X) as vectors, compute the distance "
"matrix between each pair of vectors."
msgstr "将 X 的行（以及 Y=X）视为向量，计算每对向量之间的距离矩阵。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:4 of
msgid ""
"For efficiency reasons, the euclidean distance between a pair of row "
"vector x and y is computed as::"
msgstr "出于效率考虑，行向量 x 和 y 之间的欧几里得距离计算如下："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:9 of
msgid ""
"This formulation has two advantages over other ways of computing "
"distances. First, it is computationally efficient when dealing with "
"sparse data. Second, if one argument varies but the other remains "
"unchanged, then `dot(x, x)` and/or `dot(y, y)` can be pre-computed."
msgstr ""
"这种公式与其他计算距离的方法相比有两个优势。首先，在处理稀疏数据时计算"
"效率更高。其次，如果一个参数变化而另一个保持不变，则可以预先计算 `dot(x, "
"x)` 和/或 `dot(y, y)`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:14 of
msgid ""
"However, this is not the most precise way of doing this computation, and "
"the distance matrix returned by this function may not be exactly "
"symmetric as required by, e.g., ``scipy.spatial.distance`` functions."
msgstr ""
"然而，这不是最精确的计算方法，该函数返回的距离矩阵可能不完全对称，而这在"
"例如 ``scipy.spatial.distance`` 函数中是必需的。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:18 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <metrics>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参阅 :ref:`用户指南 <metrics>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean_distances.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:24 of
msgid ""
"Pre-computed dot-products of vectors in Y (e.g., ``(Y**2).sum(axis=1)``) "
"May be ignored in some cases, see the note below."
msgstr ""
"Y 中向量的预先计算点积（例如 ``(Y**2).sum(axis=1)``），在某些情况下可能会"
"被忽略，详见下方说明。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:28 of
msgid "Return squared Euclidean distances."
msgstr "返回平方欧几里得距离。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:30 of
msgid ""
"Pre-computed dot-products of vectors in X (e.g., ``(X**2).sum(axis=1)``) "
"May be ignored in some cases, see the note below."
msgstr ""
"X 中向量的预先计算点积（例如 ``(X**2).sum(axis=1)``），在某些情况下可能会"
"被忽略，详见下方说明。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.euclidean.euclidean_distances:37 of
msgid ""
"To achieve better accuracy, `X_norm_squared` and `Y_norm_squared` may be "
"unused if they are passed as ``float32``."
msgstr ""
"为获得更高的精度，如果 `X_norm_squared` 和 `Y_norm_squared` 以 ``float32`"
"` 传递，则可能不会使用它们。"

